data.description: Charming 2 bedroom single story home nestled at the end of a cul de sac. Enjoy peace and tranquility in the large, private backyard offering views, recently installed high quality turf and only one neighboring home.  Perfect for entertaining, the spacious, open great room features beautiful wood beamed ceilings and a floor to ceiling tile fireplace. The updated kitchen with granite counters and stainless steel appliances, adds a modern touch. Other features you will appreciate are a new roof (2020), solar (2020), new tankless water heater (2022), security system with two cameras, and an updated bathroom. The second bedroom is currently being used as a dressing room/closet. Conveniently located near freeway access, local trails and parks.
